data.description:
Adorable home w/lots of charm & character. Corner lot, great Gladstone location! Walking distance of grocery store, gas station, shopping, park, highway & more! Large lot w/front & side parking perfect for entertaining. Nice walk-in closets, newer indoor paint and trim. This house is CUTE, CUTE, CUTE! Wonderful starter home- move in ready. LARGE LOT! Close to Maplewoods & Happy Rock Park. Excellent school district! Bus stop for the school is right on the corner! Gladstone road crew has a reputation for being one of the best in the area, especially during winter. 
Bring your Buyers! Don't miss this opportunity!

Sold As-is
